<h3 id="important-alert">Important alert</h3>





<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-text" data-lang="text"><span class="line"><span class="ln">1</span><span class="cl">{{&lt; important &gt;}}
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="ln">2</span><span class="cl">Crucial information necessary for users to succeed.
